this_title: The Secret Russian Space Program: The Untold Story
introduction: Many people have died to keep the Secret Space Program a secret. Many of the greatest sacrifices have been made by men and women in The Secret Russian Space Program. This three part epic movie tells the untold story of the Secret Russian Space Program and the story of the Russian Cosmonauts who secretly changed the future of space flight for all time. This is their untold story.
